BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 236.88 750 Td (UNDERSTANDING PTSD) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 740 m 552 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder \(PTSD\) is a normal response to abnormal events.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td (It is NOT a sign of weakness. It means your brain is trying to protect you.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td (WHAT CAUSES PTSD:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 651 Td (- Combat/military service        - Physical or sexual assault) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 635 Td (- Childhood abuse or neglect     - Natural disasters) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 619 Td (- Serious accidents              - Witnessing violence) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 603 Td (- Medical trauma                 - Sudden loss of loved one) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 587 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 571 Td (PTSD SYMPTOMS \(you don't need all of them\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 555 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 539 Td (RE-EXPERIENCING: Flashbacks, nightmares, intrusive memories, emotional) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 523 Td (reactions to triggers that remind you of the trauma.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 507 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 491 Td (AVOIDANCE: Avoiding places, people, activities, thoughts, or feelings) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 475 Td (associated with the trauma. Emotional numbness.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 459 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 443 Td (HYPERAROUSAL: Being on edge, easily startled, difficulty sleeping,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 427 Td (irritability, difficulty concentrating, hypervigilance.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 411 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 395 Td (NEGATIVE CHANGES IN THOUGHTS/MOOD: Negative beliefs about self/world,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 379 Td (blame, diminished interest, feeling detached, inability to feel positive.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 363 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 347 Td (IMPORTANT: PTSD is TREATABLE. Recovery is possible at any stage.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 331 Td (Effective treatments include CPT, PE, EMDR, and medication.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
