q 0 G 1 w 60 740 m 552 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (Grounding brings you back to the PRESENT when triggered.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td (TECHNIQUE 1: 5-4-3-2-1 \(Sensory Grounding\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td (Name 5 things you can SEE: ____________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 651 Td (Name 4 things you can TOUCH: __________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 635 Td (Name 3 things you can HEAR: ___________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 619 Td (Name 2 things you can SMELL: __________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 603 Td (Name 1 thing you can TASTE: ___________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 587 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 571 Td (TECHNIQUE 2: Body Scan) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 555 Td (Starting at your feet, slowly notice each body part.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 539 Td (Feet on the floor. Legs supported by the chair.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 523 Td (Hands in your lap. Shoulders dropping. Jaw unclenching.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 507 Td (Say: 'I am here. I am safe. This is now, not then.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 491 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 475 Td (TECHNIQUE 3: Safe Place Visualization) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 459 Td (Close your eyes. Imagine a place where you feel completely safe.) Tj ET
