BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 395 Td (What I feel there: _____________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 379 Td (What makes it safe: ____________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 363 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 347 Td (TECHNIQUE 4: Temperature Change) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 331 Td (Hold ice cubes, splash cold water on face, or drink cold water.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 315 Td (This activates the dive reflex and calms your nervous system.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 299 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 283 Td (TECHNIQUE 5: Mental Games) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 267 Td (Count backward from 100 by 7s. Name all 50 states.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 251 Td (List every color you can think of. Spell your name backward.) Tj ET

