BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td (EXERCISE 1: What Would You Tell a Friend?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td (If your best friend went through what you did, would you tell) Tj ET
