q 0 G 1 w 60 740 m 552 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (Sleep disruption is one of the most common PTSD symptoms.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td (Better sleep does not fix PTSD, but it makes everything easier.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td (NIGHTTIME ROUTINE \(do the same thing every night\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 651 Td (__ Set consistent bedtime: ___:___ PM) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 635 Td (__ Set consistent wake time: ___:___ AM) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 619 Td (__ Stop screens 1 hour before bed) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 603 Td (__ Dim lights in the evening) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 587 Td (__ Do calming activity: reading, gentle stretching, bath) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 571 Td (__ Keep bedroom cool \(65-68 degrees\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 555 Td (__ Use white noise or fan if needed) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 539 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 523 Td (FOR NIGHTMARES:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 507 Td (- Practice Image Rehearsal Therapy: while awake, choose a) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 491 Td (  recurring nightmare and rewrite the ending to something safe.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 475 Td (  Rehearse the new version 10-20 min daily for 2 weeks.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 459 Td (- Keep a dim nightlight if total darkness is triggering) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 443 Td (- Have grounding objects by your bed \(smooth stone, familiar scent\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 427 Td (- Upon waking from nightmare: orient to the room, name 5 objects,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 411 Td (  remind yourself 'I am safe. That was then, this is now.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 395 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 379 Td (FOR HYPERVIGILANCE AT NIGHT:) Tj ET
