BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 236.88 750 Td (FLASHBACK PROTOCOL) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 740 m 552 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (A flashback makes the past feel like it's happening NOW.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td (Use this protocol to come back to the present:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td (STEP 1: RECOGNIZE what is happening) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 651 Td (Say out loud: 'I am having a flashback. This is a memory.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 635 Td (It is not happening right now. I am safe.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 619 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 603 Td (STEP 2: GROUND yourself in the present) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 587 Td (- Stamp your feet. Feel the floor.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 571 Td (- Look around. Name the room you are in.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 555 Td (- What year is it? What day? What time?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 539 Td (- Touch something real: table, wall, your own arms.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 523 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 507 Td (STEP 3: BREATHE slowly) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 491 Td (- Breathe in for 4 counts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 475 Td (- Hold for 4 counts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 459 Td (- Breathe out for 6 counts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 443 Td (- Repeat until heart rate slows) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 427 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 411 Td (STEP 4: COMFORT yourself) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 395 Td (- Wrap yourself in a blanket) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 379 Td (- Hold a warm drink) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 363 Td (- Put on familiar, safe music) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 347 Td (- Call a safe person if needed) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 331 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 315 Td (STEP 5: RETURN to activity slowly) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 299 Td (- Don't rush. Take your time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 283 Td (- Drink water. Eat something small.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 267 Td (- You survived. You came back. You are strong.) Tj ET

endstream
