BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 221.52 750 Td (PROFESSIONAL RESOURCES) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 740 m 552 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 715 Td (This workbook is a supplement, not a replacement for therapy.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 699 Td (Here are evidence-based treatments for PTSD:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 667 Td (RECOMMENDED THERAPIES:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 651 Td (- Cognitive Processing Therapy \(CPT\): Challenges stuck points) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 635 Td (- Prolonged Exposure \(PE\): Gradually facing avoided memories) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 619 Td (- EMDR: Eye Movement Desensitization and Reprocessing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 603 Td (- Somatic Experiencing: Body-based trauma processing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 587 Td (- DBT: Dialectical Behavior Therapy \(skills for regulation\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 571 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 555 Td (HOW TO FIND A THERAPIST:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 539 Td (- Psychology Today therapist directory \(filter by 'trauma'\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 60 523 Td (- EMDR International Association directory) Tj ET
